26 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
27 number to read consecutively.
28 SUMMARY
2299 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, reduces the transfer
3300 fee proposed in the bill for the sale of a mobile home park or manufactured housing
3311 community from $50,000 per home lot to $10,000 per home lot. It increases the net worth
3322 of an entity exempt from the fee from less than $10,000,000 to less than $50,000,000. It
3333 sets out a process to collect the fee and transmit the fee to the Treasurer of State, who then
3344 credits the fee to the Manufactured Housing Community and Mobile Home Park
3355 Preservation and Assistance Fund created by the bill.
3366 FISCAL NOTE REQUIRED
3377 (See attached)
